Package io.crums.sldg.json

Class PathParser

java.lang.Object
io.crums.sldg.json.PathParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonEntityParser<Path>
public class PathParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements JsonEntityParser<Path>
Parses both lists of rows and paths. The representations are exactly the same; paths involve constraints on both the order and the row numbers.
